description: Welcome to a whirlwind of the worldliest wursts. Yummy Dog: The King of Sausage Dogs is cookin’ up top-quality hot dogs with all the toppings you would find on your travels. Go to town on the Polish Hound: Jalapeno & Cheese Kielbasa with Sauerkraut and Spicy Brown Mustard on a perfect Pretzel Bun. Enjoy the traditional tastes of the Texan: Pecan Wood Smoked Beef Sausage with Grilled Onions, Crunchy Onions, Smoked BBQ Sauce, and Pickled Jalapenos. Hurry to try the Currywurst: Pepperwurst with Black Pepper Curry Ketchup. There’s much more, so come on and get your buns over to Yummy Dog for the best wursts in Houston.
name: Yummy Dog
